author: @akanledger2174
content: Not only the ULTIMATE Queen Madonna broke another Guiness World record with the most attended stand-alone concert for any artist, but she also helped the economy greatly. Many businesses, workers there exhaled, many people are happy. She accomplished something the world leaders are not capable of doing. I also can say I am prouder to be the owner of the dress Madonna wore in Evita.
